#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'THIP.CAT_STATIS_ATR_L_V01' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


********** #WARNING# ********** Definizione della vista non trovata
CREATE VIEW THIP.CAT_STATIS_ATR_L_V01 

	AS 
		SELECT L.*, 
				ATR.NOME_TAB_AREA, 
				ATR.NOME_COLONNA  
		FROM THIP.CAT_STATIS_ATR_L L
			LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.CAT_STATIS_ATR ATR ON 
				ATR.ID_AZIENDA = L.ID_AZIENDA AND 
				ATR.ID_PROGRESSIVO = L.ID_PROGRESSIVO
GRANT ALL ON THIP.CAT_STATIS_ATR_L_V01 TO PUBLIC

Processing command file K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\5.0.0\fix\V5R1M0/40887/tddml/OFFVEN_RIG_VISTA_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.OFFVEN_RIG_VISTA_V01
CREATE
    VIEW THIP.OFFVEN_RIG_VISTA_V01 AS
	SELECT
        OVT.*,

                             CASE
		WHEN OVT.R_DEN_ABT IS NOT NULL THEN CLI.CLIRASOC
		WHEN OVT.R_SEQUENZA_IND IS NOT NULL THEN INDC.ANIRASOC
		WHEN OVT.RAGIONE_SOC_DEN IS NOT NULL THEN OVT.RAGIONE_SOC_DEN
		ELSE NULL
	END RAGIONE_SOCIALE_DEST,

                             CASE
		WHEN OVT.R_DEN_ABT IS NOT NULL THEN CLI.CLIINDIR
		WHEN OVT.R_SEQUENZA_IND IS NOT NULL THEN INDC.ANIINDIR
		WHEN OVT.RAGIONE_SOC_DEN IS NOT NULL THEN OVT.INDIRIZZO_DEN
		ELSE NULL
	END INDIRIZZO_DEST,

	CASE
		WHEN OVT.R_DEN_ABT IS NOT NULL THEN CLI.CLILOCAL
		WHEN OVT.R_SEQUENZA_IND IS NOT NULL THEN INDC.ANILOCAL
		WHEN OVT.RAGIONE_SOC_DEN IS NOT NULL THEN OVT.LOCALITA_DEN
		ELSE NULL
	END LOCALITA_DEST,

	CASE
		WHEN OVT.R_DEN_ABT IS NOT NULL THEN CLI.CLICAP
		WHEN OVT.R_SEQUENZA_IND IS NOT NULL THEN INDC.ANICAP
		WHEN OVT.RAGIONE_SOC_DEN IS NOT NULL THEN OVT.CAP_DEN
		ELSE NULL
	END CAP_DEST,

	CASE
		WHEN OVT.R_DEN_ABT IS NOT NULL THEN CLI.CLIT34CD
		WHEN OVT.R_SEQUENZA_IND IS NOT NULL THEN INDC.T34CD
		WHEN OVT.RAGIONE_SOC_DEN IS NOT NULL THEN OVT.R_NAZIONE_DEN
		ELSE NULL
	END NAZIONE_DEST,

	CASE
		WHEN OVT.R_DEN_ABT IS NOT NULL THEN CLI.CLIT35CD
		WHEN OVT.R_SEQUENZA_IND IS NOT NULL THEN INDC.T35CD
		WHEN OVT.RAGIONE_SOC_DEN IS NOT NULL THEN OVT.R_PROVINCIA_DEN
		ELSE NULL
	END PROVINCIA_DEST,

    OVR.ID_AZIENDA AZIENDA_RIG,
	OVR.ID_ANNO_OFF ID_ANNO_OFF_RIG,
	OVR.ID_NUMERO_OFF ID_NUMERO_OFF_RIG,
	OVR.ID_RIGA_OFF,
	OVR.SEQUENZA_RIGA,
	OVR.SPL_RIGA,
	OVR.ID_DET_RIGA_OFF,
	OVR.TIPO_RIGA,
	OVR.R_CAU_RIG_OFFVEN,
	OVR.R_MAGAZZINO R_MAGAZZINO_RIG,
	OVR.R_ARTICOLO,
	OVR.DES_ARTICOLO,
	OVR.DES_EXT_ARTICOLO,
	OVR.R_VERSIONE_RICH,
	OVR.R_CONFIGURAZIONE,
	OVR.R_COMMESSA COMMESSA_RIG,
	OVR.NOTA NOTA_RIG,
	OVR.R_UM_VEN,
	OVR.R_UM_PRM_MAG,
	OVR.R_UM_SEC_MAG,
	OVR.QTA_OFF_UM_VEN,
	OVR.QTA_OFF_UM_PRM,
	OVR.QTA_OFF_UM_SEC,
    OVR.QTA_ORD_UM_VEN,
	OVR.QTA_ORD_UM_PRM,
	OVR.QTA_ORD_UM_SEC,
	
  CASE 
  WHEN OVR.SALDO_MANUALE = 'Y' THEN 0
  WHEN (OVR.QTA_OFF_UM_VEN - OVR.QTA_ORD_UM_VEN) <= 0 THEN 0
  ELSE (OVR.QTA_OFF_UM_VEN - OVR.QTA_ORD_UM_VEN)
  END QTA_RES_UM_VEN,
	
  CASE
  WHEN OVR.SALDO_MANUALE = 'Y' THEN 0
  WHEN (OVR.QTA_OFF_UM_PRM - OVR.QTA_ORD_UM_PRM) <= 0 THEN 0
  ELSE (OVR.QTA_OFF_UM_PRM - OVR.QTA_ORD_UM_PRM)
  END QTA_RES_UM_PRM,
	
  CASE 
  WHEN OVR.SALDO_MANUALE = 'Y' THEN 0
  WHEN (OVR.QTA_OFF_UM_SEC - OVR.QTA_ORD_UM_SEC) <= 0 THEN 0 
  ELSE (OVR.QTA_OFF_UM_SEC - OVR.QTA_ORD_UM_SEC)
  END QTA_RES_UM_SEC,
  
	OVR.COEFF_IMPIEGO_CMP,
	OVR.DATA_CONSEG_RCS DATA_CONSEG_RCS_RIG,
	OVR.DATA_CONSEG_CFM DATA_CONSEG_CFM_RIG,
	OVR.R_LISTINO LISTINO_RIG,
	OVR.TP_RIGA_LISTINO,
	OVR.PREZZO,
	OVR.PREZZO_EXTRA,
	OVR.PREZZO_LST,
	OVR.PREZZO_EXTRA_LST,
	OVR.PREZZO_NETTO,
	OVR.R_SPESA,
	OVR.SPESA_PRC,
	OVR.IMP_PRC_SPESA,
                             OVR.R_RESPON_VENDITA R_RESPON_VENDITA_RIG,
	OVR.MAGGIORAZIONE,
	OVR.SCONTO_ART1,
	OVR.SCONTO_ART2,
	OVR.R_SCONTO R_SCONTO_RIG,
	OVR.SCONTO_CLI SCONTO_CLI_RIG,
	OVR.SCONTO_MOD SCONTO_MOD_RIG,
	OVR.R_SCONTO_MOD R_SCONTO_MOD_RIG,
	OVR.R_ASSOG_IVA R_ASSOG_IVA_RIG,
	OVR.UM_PREZZO,
	OVR.TP_PREZZO,
	OVR.PROVENIENZA_PREZZO,
	OVR.BLO_RCL_PRZ_S_FAT,
	OVR.R_AGENTE R_AGENTE_RIG,
	OVR.PVG1_AGENTE PVG1_AGENTE_RIG,
	OVR.PVG2_AGENTE PVG2_AGENTE_RIG,
	OVR.R_AGENTE_SUB R_AGENTE_SUB_RIG,
	OVR.PVG1_SUB_AGENTE PVG1_SUB_AGENTE_RIG,
	OVR.PVG2_SUB_AGENTE PVG2_SUB_AGENTE_RIG,
	OVR.R_CENTRO_COSTO R_CENTRO_COSTO_RIG,
	OVR.COS_UNITARIO_ART,
	OVR.COSTO_RIFER,
	OVR.COS_ORDINATO COS_ORDINATO_RIG,
                             OVR.COS_OFFERTO COS_OFFERTO_RIG,
	OVR.VLR_ORDINATO VLR_ORDINATO_RIG,
                             OVR.VLR_OFFERTO VLR_OFFERTO_RIG,
                             OVR.VLR_IMPOSTA_ORD VLR_IMPOSTA_ORD_RIG,
	OVR.VLR_IMPOSTA_OFF VLR_IMPOSTA_OFF_RIG,
                             OVR.VLR_ORD_TOT_RIGA,
	OVR.VLR_OFF_TOT_RIGA,
                             OVR.R_ANNO_ORD R_ANNO_ORD_RIG,
                             OVR.R_RIGA_ORD R_RIGA_ORD_RIG,
                             OVR.R_NUMERO_ORD R_NUMERO_ORD_RIG,
	OVR.NO_FATTURA,
	OVR.STATO_PCD,
	OVR.STATO STATO_RIG,
	OVR.STATO_AVANZAMENTO STATO_AVANZAMENTO_RIG,
	OVR.STATO_EVASIONE STATO_EVASIONE_RIG,
	OVR.SALDO_MANUALE SALDO_MANUALE_RIG,
        OVR.R_CONCOR_OFF R_CONCOR_OFF_RIG,
        OVR.R_PROD_CONCOR R_PROD_CONCOR_RIG,
        OVR.R_CAU_CHR_OFFVEN R_CAU_CHR_OFFVEN_RIG,
	OVR.R_BENE R_BENE_RIG,
	OVR.R_ANNO_RCS_SRV R_ANNO_RCS_SRV_RIG,
	OVR.R_NUMERO_RCS_SRV R_NUMERO_RCS_SRV_RIG,
	OVR.PRZ_CONCORDATO,
	ARTCLI.ID_NUMERATORE NUM_ARTICOLO_CLI,
    ARTCLI.ARTICOLO_CLI,
	ARTCLI.DESCRIZIONE DESC_ARTICOLO_CLI

        FROM
	    THIP.OFF_VEN_TES     OVT
	INNER JOIN
	    THIP.OFF_VEN_RIG   OVR
		ON (
			OVT.ID_AZIENDA = OVR.ID_AZIENDA AND
			OVT.ID_ANNO_OFF = OVR.ID_ANNO_OFF AND
			OVT.ID_NUMERO_OFF = OVR.ID_NUMERO_OFF
		)

                LEFT OUTER JOIN
	    FINANCE.BBCLIPT CLI
		ON (
			CLI.T01CD =  OVT.ID_AZIENDA AND
			CLI.CLICD = OVT.R_DEN_ABT
		)
	        LEFT OUTER JOIN
	    FINANCE.BBANIPT INDC
		ON (
			OVT.R_ANAGRAFICO=INDC.ANACD AND
			OVT.R_SEQUENZA_IND=INDC.ANICD
		)
		LEFT OUTER JOIN 
		THIP.ARTICOLI_CLI ARTCLI
		ON (
			OVT.ID_AZIENDA = ARTCLI.ID_AZIENDA AND 
			OVT.R_CLIENTE = ARTCLI.R_CLIENTE AND 
			OVR.R_ARTICOLO = ARTCLI.R_ARTICOLO AND			
			(OVR.R_CONFIGURAZIONE = ARTCLI.R_CONFIGURAZIONE OR 
			(OVR.R_CONFIGURAZIONE IS NULL AND ARTCLI.R_CONFIGURAZIONE IS NULL ))
		)
GRANT ALL ON THIP.OFFVEN_RIG_VISTA_V01 TO PUBLIC

		D.TP_FONTE_DOC,
		D.STT_AVVSPE,
		D.GESTIONE_PPL,
		D.R_GERARCHIA,
		D.STATO_PPL,
		D.STT_PICKING,
		D.STT_PACKING,
		D.STT_STP_PICKING,

		D.ID_ANNO_DOC_IC,
		D.ID_NUMERO_DOC_IC,
		D.GEN_INTCMP,
		D.TARGA_MEZZO,
		D.VOLUME,
		D.RIC_PESIVOL,
		D.FATTURA_PA,
		D.ID_LINEA_CREDITO,
		D.SPLIT_PAYMENT,
		D.RIF_AMMINISTR,
		D.GES_DES_FATTURA_PA,
		D.ID_DOC_SM,
		D.NUM_DOC_SM,
		D.GES_DEPERIBILI,
		D.R_AGGREG_DDT,
		D.RAGGRUPPA_DDT,
		D.STT_RICPV_PRIMA_STPBOL,
		D.INDIRIZZO_PEC,
		D.ID_DESTIN_FAT,
		V.TIPO_BENE_DEP,
		CM.CODICE_CIG,
		CM.CODICE_CUP,
		D.RITENUTA_ACC,
		CASE
		WHEN (NOT D.R_CAU_CONTABILE IS NULL)
			THEN D.R_CAU_CONTABILE
        WHEN (NOT G.R_CAU_CONTABILE IS NULL)
			THEN G.R_CAU_CONTABILE
        ELSE C.R_CAU_CONTABILE
    END AS CAU_CONTABILE,
		D.SCN_FINALE_FAT,
		D.PRC_SCNFIN_FAT,
		D.TOT_SCN_FIN_FAT
FROM 
    THIP.DOC_VEN_TES D 
JOIN
    THIP.CAU_DOCVEN C
ON
    C.ID_AZIENDA = D.ID_AZIENDA
AND C.ID_CAU_DOC_VEN = D.R_CAU_DOC_VEN

LEFT OUTER JOIN 
	THIP.DOCVEN_TP_BENE_V01 V 
ON 
    D.ID_AZIENDA = V.ID_AZIENDA AND
    D.ID_ANNO_DOC = V.ID_ANNO_DOC AND
    D.ID_NUMERO_DOC = V.ID_NUMERO_DOC
	
LEFT OUTER JOIN
    THIP.COMMESSE CM
ON
    D.ID_AZIENDA = CM.ID_AZIENDA AND 
	D.R_COMMESSA = CM.ID_COMMESSA

LEFT OUTER JOIN
    THIP.CAU_DOCVEN_CAT G
ON
    D.ID_AZIENDA = G.ID_AZIENDA1
AND D.R_CAU_DOC_VEN = G.ID_CAU_DOC_VEN
AND D.R_CAT_CONT_CLI = G.ID_CAT_CON_CLI

WHERE 
    D.STATO                = 'V' 
    AND D.STATO_AVANZAMENTO= '2' 
    AND D.TP_BLOCCO_LSP   <> 'I' 
    AND D.TIPO_BOLLA       = '2'

Processing command file K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\5.0.0\fix\V5R1M0/40972/tddml/INVENTARIO_RIG_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.INVENTARIO_RIG_V01
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'THIP.INVENTARIO_RIG_V01' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


********** #WARNING# ********** Definizione della vista non trovata
CREATE VIEW THIP.INVENTARIO_RIG_V01 

	AS SELECT I.ID_AZIENDA, S.ID_SALDO_UBI, MAX(I.TIMESTAMP_RILEV) AS TIMESTAMP_RILEV
	FROM  THIP.INVENTARIO_RIG I, THIP.SALDI_UBICAZIONE S
	WHERE STATO= 'V' AND STATO_INV='F' 
	AND S.ID_AZIENDA = I.ID_AZIENDA   
	AND S.ID_MAGAZZINO = I.R_MAGAZZINO 
	AND S.ID_UBICAZIONE= I.R_UBICAZIONE 	
	AND S.ID_ARTICOLO = I.R_ARTICOLO 
	AND S.ID_VERSIONE = I.R_VERSIONE 
	AND S.ID_CONFIG = I.R_CONFIG 
	AND (S.ID_COMMESSA= I.R_COMMESSA 	OR (S.ID_COMMESSA IS NULL AND I.R_COMMESSA IS NULL))  
	AND (S.ID_CLIENTE= I.R_CLIENTE 	OR  (S.ID_CLIENTE IS NULL AND I.R_CLIENTE IS NULL))  
	AND (S.ID_MATRICOLA= I.R_MATRICOLA 	OR (S.ID_MATRICOLA IS NULL AND I.R_MATRICOLA IS NULL))  
	AND S.ID_LOTTO = I.R_LOTTO
	GROUP BY I.ID_AZIENDA, I.R_MAGAZZINO, I.R_UBICAZIONE, I.R_ARTICOLO, I.R_VERSIONE, I.R_CONFIG, I.R_LOTTO, I.R_COMMESSA, I.R_CLIENTE, I.R_MATRICOLA, S.ID_SALDO_UBI

CREATE TABLE THIP.GWMST00F
(
   MWSTAT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'V',
   MWTSUIE DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   MWTSCRZ DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   MWTSAGG DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   MWUTCRZ CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   MWUTAGG CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   MWCFUN CHAR(1) NOT NULL,
   MWPARAM TEXT,
   MWSQL TEXT,
   MWDESF CHAR(30) NOT NULL,
   MWIDAZ CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   VALID_MSG_TMPL CHAR(15),
   ERROR_MSG_TMPL CHAR(15),
CONSTRAINT GWMSTE2MSGTMPL FOREIGN KEY (ERROR_MSG_TMPL)
        REFERENCES THERA.MSG_TMPL,
CONSTRAINT GWMSTV2MSGTMPL FOREIGN KEY (VALID_MSG_TMPL)
        REFERENCES THERA.MSG_TMPL
)  ON 'THIP8'
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX GWMST00F_PK ON THIP.GWMST00F (MWIDAZ ASC, MWCFUN ASC)
ALTER TABLE THIP.GWMST00F ADD PRIMARY KEY  (MWIDAZ, MWCFUN)
GRANT ALL ON THIP.GWMST00F TO PUBLIC

DROP VIEW THIP.VARIAZCST_V04
CREATE VIEW THIP.VARIAZCST_V04 AS SELECT ART.*, 
CASE 
    	WHEN CNF.ID_CONFIG IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE CNF.ID_CONFIG
END	ID_CONFIG, 
CNF.COD_CONFIG FROM THIP.ARTICOLI ART LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.CONFIGURAZIONI CNF ON ART.ID_AZIENDA = CNF.ID_AZIENDA AND ART.ID_ARTICOLO = CNF.R_ARTICOLO

Processing command file K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\5.0.0\fix\V5R1M0/41486/tddml/FPPRO00F_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.FPPRO00F_V01
CREATE VIEW THIP.FPPRO00F_V01 

		AS SELECT 
			FPP.PZ_KEYPRGINVIO AS PZ_KEYPRGINVIO, 
			FPP.PZ_KEYHEADERFATT AS PZ_KEYHEADERFATT, 
			FPP.PZ_KEYBODYFATT AS PZ_KEYBODYFATT, 
			FPP.PZ_AMBIENTE AS PZ_AMBIENTE, 
			SUBSTRING(FPP.PZ_SETGEST, 1, 1) AS PZ_SETGEST , 
			FPP.PZ_UTEGEST AS PZ_UTEGEST ,
			FPP.PZ_DATAORARIC AS PZ_DATAORARIC,
			FPP.PZ_TIPOREGCONT AS PZ_TIPOREGCONT,	
			CONVERT(datetime,FPP.PZ_DATAREGCONT) AS PZ_DATAREGCONT,		
			FPP.PZ_NUMREGCONT AS PZ_NUMREGCONT,
			FPP.PZ_DATAPROT AS PZ_DATAPROT,
			FPP.PZ_ANNOPROT AS PZ_ANNOPROT,
			FPP.PZ_NUMPROT AS PZ_NUMPROT,
			FPP.PZ_CODSDI

			FROM THIP.FPPRO00F FPP

Processing command file K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\5.0.0\fix\V5R1M0/41539/tddml/MODPRO_ATV_MAT_V03.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.MODPRO_ATV_MAT_V03
CREATE 
    VIEW THIP.MODPRO_ATV_MAT_V03 AS 
SELECT 
    THIP.MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA         AS ID_AZIENDA, 
    THIP.MODPRO.ID_MODELLO         AS ID_MODELLO, 
    A.ID_ARTICOLO                  AS R_ARTICOLO_PADRE, 
    A.LIVELLO_MIN_MODEL            AS LIV_MIN_PADRE, 
    THIP.MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_ARTICOLO AS R_MATERIALE, 
    B.LIVELLO_MIN_MODEL            AS LIVELLO_MIN_MODEL, 
    B.LIVELLO_MIN_LAV              AS LIVELLO_MIN_LAV 
FROM 
    THIP.MODPRO, 
    THIP.MODPRO_ATV_MAT, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI A, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI B 
WHERE 
    THIP.MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA             = THIP.MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND THIP.MODPRO.ID_MODELLO         = THIP.MODPRO_ATV_MAT.ID_MODELLO 
    AND THIP.MODPRO.TIPO_MODELLO      <> '2' 
    AND THIP.MODPRO.TIPO_MODELLO      <> '5' 
	AND THIP.MODPRO.TIPO_MODELLO      <> '7' 
    AND THIP.MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA         = A.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND THIP.MODPRO.R_ARTICOLO         = A.ID_ARTICOLO 
    AND THIP.MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA         = B.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND THIP.MODPRO_ATV_MAT.R_ARTICOLO = B.ID_ARTICOLO
GRANT ALL ON THIP.MODPRO_ATV_MAT_V03 TO PUBLIC

Processing command file K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\5.0.0\fix\V5R1M0/41539/tddml/MODPRO_ATV_PRD_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.MODPRO_ATV_PRD_V01
CREATE 
    VIEW THIP.MODPRO_ATV_PRD_V01 AS 
SELECT 
    THIP.MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA         AS ID_AZIENDA, 
    THIP.MODPRO.ID_MODELLO         AS ID_MODELLO, 
    A.ID_ARTICOLO                  AS R_ARTICOLO_PADRE, 
    A.LIVELLO_MIN_MODEL            AS LIV_MIN_PADRE, 
    THIP.MODPRO_ATV_PRD.R_ARTICOLO AS R_PRODOTTO, 
    B.LIVELLO_MIN_MODEL            AS LIVELLO_MIN_MODEL, 
    B.LIVELLO_MIN_LAV              AS LIVELLO_MIN_LAV 
FROM 
    THIP.MODPRO, 
    THIP.MODPRO_ATV_PRD, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI A, 
    THIP.ARTICOLI B 
WHERE 
    THIP.MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA        = THIP.MODPRO_ATV_PRD.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND THIP.MODPRO.ID_MODELLO    = THIP.MODPRO_ATV_PRD.ID_MODELLO 
    AND THIP.MODPRO.R_ARTICOLO   <> THIP.MODPRO_ATV_PRD.R_ARTICOLO 
    AND THIP.MODPRO.TIPO_MODELLO <> '2' 
    AND THIP.MODPRO.TIPO_MODELLO <> '5' 
	AND THIP.MODPRO.TIPO_MODELLO <> '7' 
    AND THIP.MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA    = A.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND 
    (
        THIP.MODPRO.R_ARTICOLO    = A.ID_ARTICOLO 
        OR THIP.MODPRO.R_ARTICOLO = A.R_GRP_MODELLO
    ) 
    AND THIP.MODPRO.ID_AZIENDA         = B.ID_AZIENDA 
    AND THIP.MODPRO_ATV_PRD.R_ARTICOLO = B.ID_ARTICOLO
GRANT ALL ON THIP.MODPRO_ATV_PRD_V01 TO PUBLIC

Processing command file K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\5.0.0\fix\V5R1M0/41090/tddml/C10_O01A.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.C10_O01A
CREATE VIEW THIP.C10_O01A AS 
SELECT
	ID_PROGRESSIVO AS IDO01A,
	CAUSALE_LOG AS IKCAULOG,
	ID_RUN AS IKRUNIMP,
	CASE
		WHEN TIPO_OPERAZIONE = 'D' THEN 'D'
		ELSE 'U'
	END AS FAZI,
	ID_AZIENDA AS TH_AZIENDA,
	ID_AMBIENTE_NIC AS TH_AMBIENTE,
	R_STABILIMENTO AS TH_STABILIMENTO,
	CAST(STATO_PRC AS SMALLINT) AS TH_FREAD,
	GRUPPO AS CSTR,
	TP_ORDINE AS TH_PRD_ACQ,
	ID_ORDINE AS CPRD,
	ID_ARTICOLO AS CART,
        R_FORNITORE AS CCIC,
        TEMPO_APV_LOT_MIN AS CVER,
	'30' AS TIPORD,
	STATO_ORDINE AS FLGSTA,
	R_MAG_VERSAMENTO AS CMAG,
	DATA_INZ_RCS AS DPRICHI,
	DATA_FIN_RCS AS DPRICHF,
	QTA_RCS_UM_PRM AS QPORD,
	QTA_VRS_UM_PRM AS QPMAG,
	R_FAMIGLIA_PGM AS OPPRI,
	R_CLIENTE AS CCLI,
	R_COMMESSA AS TH_COMMESSA,
	COD_CONFIG AS TH_CCONFIG,
	R_UTENTE_CRZ AS TH_UTE_CRZ,
    R_UTENTE_AGG AS TH_UTE_AGG,
    TIMESTAMP_CRZ AS TH_TS_CRZ,
    TIMESTAMP_AGG AS TH_TS_AGG
FROM
	THIP.C10_ORDESE

Processing command file K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\5.0.0\fix\V5R1M0/41090/tddml/C10_T01A.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.C10_T01A
CREATE VIEW THIP.C10_T01A AS
SELECT P01A.*, CFG.COD_CONFIG AS TH_CCONFIG
FROM THIP.C10_P01A P01A
LEFT JOIN THIP.CONFIGURAZIONI CFG
ON P01A.TH_AZIENDA=CFG.ID_AZIENDA AND P01A.CART = CFG.R_ARTICOLO

Processing command file K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\5.0.0\fix\V5R1M0/41090/tddml/C10_T01P.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.C10_T01P
CREATE VIEW THIP.C10_T01P AS
SELECT P01P.*, CFG.COD_CONFIG AS TH_CCONFIG
FROM THIP.C10_P01P P01P
LEFT JOIN THIP.CONFIGURAZIONI CFG
ON P01P.TH_AZIENDA=CFG.ID_AZIENDA AND P01P.CART = CFG.R_ARTICOLO

Processing command file K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\5.0.0\fix\V5R1M0/41732/tddml/VARIAZCST_V02.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.VARIAZCST_V02
CREATE 
    VIEW THIP.VARIAZCST_V02 AS 
SELECT 
    SALDI.*, 
    ART.ID_ARTICOLO AS R_ARTICOLO, 
    ART.TIPO_PARTE, 
    ART.R_LINEA_PROD AS R_LINEA_PRODOTTO, 
    ART.R_MACROFAMIGLIA, 
    ART.R_MICROFAMIGLIA, 
    ART.R_SUBFAMIGLIA, 
    ART.R_CLASSE_MERCLG, 
    ART.R_CLS_MATERIALE, 
    ART.R_PIANIFICATORE,
	ART.R_CLASSE_FISCALE , 
   	ART.R_GRP_PRODOTTO  ,
   	ART.R_CLASSE_A ,
   	ART.R_CLASSE_B ,
   	ART.R_CLASSE_C ,
   	ART.R_CLASSE_D ,
   	ART.R_CLASSE_E 
FROM 
    THIP.SALDI_BASE SALDI 
JOIN 
    THIP.ARTICOLI ART 
    ON 
    (
        SALDI.ID_AZIENDA      = ART.ID_AZIENDA 
        AND SALDI.ID_ARTICOLO = ART.ID_ARTICOLO
    )
GRANT ALL ON THIP.VARIAZCST_V02 TO PUBLIC

CLIV.NOTA , CLIV.R_GES_COMMENTI , CLIV.R_ANAGRAFICO , CLIV.R_SEQUENZA_IND , CLIV.R_DEN_ABT , CLIV.R_CLIENTE_FAT , CLIV.R_FORNITORE , CLIV.R_CAU_ORD_VEN , CLIV.R_CAU_DOC_VEN , CLIV.PRIORITA , CLIV.R_LISTINO_PRZ , CLIV.R_LISTINO_PRZ_ALT , CLIV.R_SPESA1 , CLIV.R_SPESA2 , CLIV.SCONTO_CLI , CLIV.SCONTO_MOD , CLIV.R_SCONTO , CLIV.R_AGENTE , CLIV.PVG_AGENTE , CLIV.R_AGENTE_SUB , CLIV.PVG_AGENTE_SUB , CASE WHEN CLIV.TP_LIQ_PVG IS NULL THEN 'G' ELSE CLIV.TP_LIQ_PVG END , CLIV.R_MOD_SPEDIZIONE , CLIV.R_MOD_CONSEGNA , CLIV.R_ASPETTO_ESN , CLIV.R_CAU_TRASPORTO , CLIV.VETTORE1 , CLIV.R_CALENDARIO , CLIV.R_GIRO_CONSEGNE , CASE WHEN CLIV.RAG_ORD_BOLLA IS NULL THEN 'Y' ELSE CLIV.RAG_ORD_BOLLA END , CASE WHEN CLIV.RAG_BOLLE_FAT IS NULL THEN 'Y' ELSE CLIV.RAG_BOLLE_FAT END , CASE WHEN CLIV.FRZ_BOLLA_FAT IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE CLIV.FRZ_BOLLA_FAT END , CASE WHEN CLIV.RIF_DATA_PRZ_SCN IS NULL THEN '3' ELSE CLIV.RIF_DATA_PRZ_SCN END , CASE WHEN CLIV.TP_SPLIT_PAYMENT IS NULL THEN '1' ELSE CLIV.TP_SPLIT_PAYMENT END , CASE WHEN CLIV.RCL_PRZ_SCN_FAT IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE CLIV.RCL_PRZ_SCN_FAT END , CASE WHEN CLIV.CONDIZ_FAT IS NULL THEN '1' ELSE CLIV.CONDIZ_FAT END , CASE WHEN CLIV.FAT_SOSPESA IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE CLIV.FAT_SOSPESA END , CASE WHEN CLIV.FAT_PERIODICA IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE CLIV.FAT_PERIODICA END , CLIV.R_ASSOG_IVA , CASE WHEN CLIV.ADDEBITO_IVA_OMF IS NULL THEN '-' ELSE CLIV.ADDEBITO_IVA_OMF END , CLIV.R_RESPON_VENDITE , CLIV.FLAG_CONAI , CLIV.R_CAT_CONT_CLI , CLIV.R_GRP_CNT_CA , CLIV.R_GRP_CNT_SPC_CA , CASE WHEN CLIV.ADB_SPS_INCASSO IS NULL THEN 'Y' ELSE CLIV.ADB_SPS_INCASSO END , CASE WHEN CLIV.ADB_SPS_BO_NO_IVA IS NULL THEN 'Y' ELSE CLIV.ADB_SPS_BO_NO_IVA END , CASE WHEN CLIV.ADB_SPS_BO_RCV IS NULL THEN 'Y' ELSE CLIV.ADB_SPS_BO_RCV END , CASE WHEN CLIV.ADB_SPS_BO_EFT IS NULL THEN 'Y' ELSE CLIV.ADB_SPS_BO_EFT END , CLIV.R_BLOCCO_ORD , CLIV.R_BLOCCO_EVAS , CLIV.R_DOCUMENTO_MM , CLIV.ATTRIBUTI_ESTEND , CLIV.ESCLUDI_CTRL_FIDO , CLIV.R_POLITICA_FIDO , CASE WHEN CLIV.STATO IS NULL THEN 'I' ELSE CLIV.STATO END , CLIV.R_UTENTE_CRZ , CLIV.R_UTENTE_AGG , CLIV.TIMESTAMP_CRZ , CLIV.TIMESTAMP_AGG, CLI.T54CD,   CLI.T31CD

			 ,CLI.CLIFIMAS, CLI.CLIFDLVA, CLI.CLITPVAL, CLI.T42CD, CLI.T16CD, CLI.T30CD, CLI.T40CD, CLI.T05CD, CLI.T33CD, CLI.T29CD,

			 CLI.CLIESTSO, CLI.T19CD, CLI.CLIERIBA, CLI.ANICD, CLI.VOCCD, CLI.CLICORI2, CLI.CLICORI3, CLI.CLICORI4, CLI.CLICORI5, CLI.CLINDINT, CLI.CLIDDIIN, CLI.CLINPDIN,
			 CLI.CLIDTPRI, CLI.CLICFINT, CLI.CLICLDIP, CLI.CLIIVADF, CLI.CLIGGEM1, CLI.CLIGGEM2, CLI.CLIGGEM3, CLI.CLIGGEM4, CLI.CLIGGEM5, CLI.CLIIVDIN, CLI.CLIFVDIN,
			 CLI.CLIGGCAS, CLI.ANRCD, CLI.CLICORSO, CLI.CLICORRI, CLI.CLIDTINI, CLI.CLIDTFIN,
			
			CLIV.CODICE_CLI_EDI, CLIV.CODICE_EORI_CLI, CLIV.DEST_FATT_PA, CLIV.R_GERARCHIA, CLIV.INDIRIZZO_PEC, CLIV.RAGGRUPPA_DDT, CLIV.RIF_AMMINISTR, CLIV.TITOLO_CLI	
			,CLIV.R_CAU_OFF_VEN,CLI.DIZSTATO,CLIV.WF_CLASS_ID,CLIV.WF_ID,CLIV.WF_NODE_ID,CLIV.WF_SUB_NODE_ID,WCN.DESCRIPTION DESC_NODO,WSP.DESCRIPTION WF_DESC, CLIV.PAESE_RAPP_FISC, CLIV.R_FORN_RAPP_FISC 
			
	FROM FINANCE.BBCLIPT CLI 
		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.CLIENTI_VEN CLIV ON 
			CLIV.ID_AZIENDA = CLI.T01CD AND 
			CLIV.ID_CLIENTE = CLI.CLICD
		LEFT OUTER JOIN THERA.WF_CLASS_NODE WCN ON
			WCN.WF_CLASS_ID = CLIV.WF_CLASS_ID
			AND WCN.NODE_ID = CLIV.WF_NODE_ID
		LEFT OUTER JOIN THERA.WF_SPEC WSP ON
			WSP.WF_CLASS_ID = CLIV.WF_CLASS_ID
			AND WSP.WF_ID = CLIV.WF_ID

DROP TABLE FINANCE.BCRIMPT
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BCRIMPT' di tipo tabella, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE TABLE FINANCE.BCRIMPT
(
   T01CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   RILDTCHC DATETIME NOT NULL,
   T09CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   MOVNUREG NUMERIC(7,0) NOT NULL,
   MOVNRIRE NUMERIC(7,0) NOT NULL,
   T06CD CHAR(3),
   MOVDTIVA DATETIME,
   T07CD CHAR(3),
   MOVNPIVA NUMERIC(7,0),
   MOVDTRCO DATETIME,
   MOVDTDOC DATETIME,
   RIMNRDOC CHAR(20),
   CLICD CHAR(8),
   FORCD CHAR(8),
   ANARASOC CHAR(35),
   MOVIIVVP NUMERIC(17,2),
   T05CD CHAR(3),
   MOVALIVA NUMERIC(5,2),
   MOVIVAVP NUMERIC(15,2),
   T02CD CHAR(3),
   MOVDSCAU CHAR(35),
   MOVQCRVP NUMERIC(17,2),
   RIMTPLIQ CHAR(1),
   WRKTLIPE CHAR(1),
   RIMSQNMO CHAR(35),
   RIMSQPED CHAR(35),
   RIMSQIND NUMERIC(17,2),
   RIMSQLIV NUMERIC(17,2),
   RIMSQLIA NUMERIC(17,2)
)  ON 'FINANCE4'
ALTER TABLE FINANCE.BCRIMPT ADD CONSTRAINT BCRIMPT_IX PRIMARY KEY (T01CD, RILDTCHC, T09CD, MOVNUREG, MOVNRIRE )
GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BCRIMPT TO PUBLIC

CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BCRILVG (
	T01CD,
	RILDTCHC,
	RILPAPRO,
	YLI74TVP,
	T40CD,
	RIDOATVP,
    RIDOPAVP,
    RIDAUAVP,
    RIDTVEVP,
    RIDTACVP,
    RIDICPVP,
    RIDIDPVP,
    RILVICVP,
    RILULDVP,
    RILIVNVP,
    RILIVEVP,
    RILIVEVS,
	RILICRVP,
    RILIDBVP,
    RILIRBVP,
	RIDC12VP,
    RIDD12VP,
    RILCIUVP,
    RILPMITR,
	RIDILTVP,
    RILACIVP,
    RIDVERSA,
	RIDVEREU,
    RIDLIQTR,
	RIDRIMBO,
    RIDF24VP,
    RIDF24VS,
    RIDTPLIQ
) AS
SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.RILDTCHC,
    T1.RILPAPRO,
    T1.YLI74TVP,
    T1.T40CD,
	T2.RIDOATVP,
    T2.RIDOPAVP,
    T2.RIDAUAVP,
    T2.RIDTVEVP,
	T2.RIDTACVP,
    T2.RIDICPVP,
    T2.RIDIDPVP,
    T2.RILVICVP,
    T2.RILULDVP,
    T2.RILIVNVP,
    T2.RILIVEVP,
    T2.RILIVEVS,
	T2.RILICRVP,
    T2.RILIDBVP,
    T2.RILIRBVP,
    T2.RIDC12VP,
    T2.RIDD12VP,
	T2.RILCIUVP,
    T2.RILPMITR,
	T2.RIDILTVP,
	T2.RILACIVP,
    T2.RIDVERSA,
    T2.RIDVEREU,
    T2.RIDLIQTR,
    T2.RIDRIMBO,
	T2.RIDF24VP,
    T2.RIDF24VS,
    T2.RIDTPLIQ
FROM FINANCE.BCRILPT T1
INNER JOIN FINANCE.BCRIDPT T2  ON
		T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
        T1.RILDTCHC = T2.RIDDTCHC

Processing command file K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\5.0.0\fix\V5R1M0/41962/primrose/script/04BCRIMVG.TDDML.
DROP VIEW FINANCE.BCRIMVG 
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BCRIMVG' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BCRIMVG (
    T01CD,
    RILDTCHC,
    T09CD,
    MOVNUREG,
    MOVNRIRE,
    T06CD,
    MOVDTIVA,
    T07CD,
    MOVNPIVA,
    MOVDTRCO,
    MOVDTDOC,
    RIMNRDOC,
    CLICD,
    FORCD,
    ANARASOC,
    MOVIIVVP,
    T05CD,
    MOVALIVA,
    MOVIVAVP,
    T02CD,
    MOVDSCAU,
    MOVQCRVP,
    RIMTPLIQ,
    WRKTLIPE,
    RIMSQNMO,
    RIMSQPED,
    RIMSQIND,
    RIMSQLIV,
    RIMSQLIA,
	RIMIMPSE,
	RIMIVASE,
	RIMSEZIO
)
AS
SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.RILDTCHC,
    T1.T09CD,
    T1.MOVNUREG,
    T1.MOVNRIRE,
    T1.T06CD,
    T1.MOVDTIVA,
    T1.T07CD,
    T1.MOVNPIVA,
    T1.MOVDTRCO,
    T1.MOVDTDOC,
    T1.RIMNRDOC,
    T1.CLICD,
    T1.FORCD,
    T1.ANARASOC,
    T1.MOVIIVVP,
    T1.T05CD,
    T1.MOVALIVA,
    T1.MOVIVAVP,
    T1.T02CD,
    T1.MOVDSCAU,
    T1.MOVQCRVP,
    T1.RIMTPLIQ,
    T1.WRKTLIPE,
    T1.RIMSQNMO,
    T1.RIMSQPED,
    T1.RIMSQIND,
    T1.RIMSQLIV,
    T1.RIMSQLIA,
	( CASE  
      WHEN T1.RIMTPLIQ = '1' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = '2' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = '3' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = '4' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = '5' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = 'B' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = 'C' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = 'E' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = 'G' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = 'I' 
	  THEN T1.MOVIIVVP
      ELSE 0 - T1.MOVIIVVP END 
     ), 
	( CASE  
      WHEN T1.RIMTPLIQ = '1' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = '2' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = '3' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = '4' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = '5' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = 'B' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = 'C' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = 'E' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = 'G' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = 'I' 
	  THEN T1.MOVIVAVP
      ELSE 0 - T1.MOVIVAVP END 
     ),
	( CASE  
      WHEN T1.RIMTPLIQ = '1' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = '2' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = '3' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = '4' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = '5' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = 'B' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = 'C' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = 'E' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = 'G' OR T1.RIMTPLIQ = 'I' 
	  THEN 'V'
      ELSE 'A' END 
     )
FROM FINANCE.BCRIMPT T1

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BCMOVVG 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BCMOVVG AS
SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T09CD,
    T1.MOVNUREG,
    T1.MOVNRIRE,
    T1.MOVSTATO,
    T1.DIZUTCRE,

    T1.DIZHHCRE,

    T1.MOVIMPVS,

    T1.MOVIMPVE,

    T1.MOVCAMBVS,
    T1.T02CD,
    T1.MOVTICAU,
    T1.MOVDSCAU,
    T1.MOVDSAGG,
    T1.MOVIVA,
    T1.T05CD,
    T1.T07CD,
    T1.T06CD,
    T1.MOVIIVVP,
    T1.MOVIVADF,
    T1.MOVIIVVS,
    T1.MOVIVAVP,
    T1.MOVIVAVS,
    T1.MOVALIVA,
    T1.MOVFQIVA,
    T1.MOVIVAVM,
    T1.MOVIIVVE,
    T1.MOVIVAVE,
    T1.MOVQCRVP,
    T1.MOVQCRVS,
    T1.MOVQIVVP,
    T1.MOVQIVVS,
    T1.MOVQCRVE,
    T1.MOVQIVVE,
    T1.MOVTCFCO,
    T1.MOVCLICO,
    T1.MOVVOCCC,
    T1.FORCNTRP,
    T1.MOVCOMUL,
    T1.T22CD,
    T1.FOBNPROG,
    T1.CLBNPROG,
    T1.T39CD,
    T1.T38CDABI,
    T1.T38CDCAB,
    T1.MOVABCAB,
    T1.MOVNCCOR,
    T1.MOVCCIN,
    T1.MOVBIC,
    T1.MOVIBAN,
    T1.T40CD,
    T1.T36CD,
    T1.FORSOFAC,
    T1.T30CD,
    T1.T28CD,
    T1.T66TPCNT,
    T1.MOVT61CD,
    T1.MOVVCACD,
    T1.MOVT62CD,
    T1.MOVQUREG,
    T1.MOVNRIGI,
    T1.MOVDTCHC,
    T1.MOVNPCAD,
    T1.MOVDTCHI,
    T1.MOVNPIAD,
    T1.MOVDTESC,
    T1.MOVINUSO,
    T1.MOVTPMOV,
    T1.MOVDAPRE,
    T1.T97CD,
    T1.MOVFLG1,
    T1.MOVFLG2,
    T1.MOVFLG3,
    T1.MOVIMPLB,
    T1.MOVDTLB, 
    ( CASE  
      WHEN (T1.MOVINUSO='1') THEN 'X'  
      WHEN (T1.MOVSTATO='1') THEN '1'  
      WHEN (T1.MOVSTATO='2') THEN '2' 
      WHEN (T1.MOVSTATO='4') THEN '4' 
      WHEN (T1.MOVSTATO='5') THEN '5' 
      ELSE '0'  END
     ) AS MOTIC1, 
    (CASE 
      WHEN (COALESCE(T2.MOVDINCO, CONVERT(DATETIME, '1753-01-01', 120))<>CONVERT(DATETIME, '1753-01-01', 120)) THEN T2.MOVDINCO 
      ELSE T1.MOVDTRCO END 
     ) AS MOVDINCO, 
    (CASE 
      WHEN (COALESCE(T2.MOVDFICO, CONVERT(DATETIME, '1753-01-01', 120))<>CONVERT(DATETIME, '1753-01-01', 120)) THEN T2.MOVDFICO 
      ELSE T1.MOVDTRCO END 
     ) AS MOVDFICO 
FROM FINANCE.BCMOVPT T1 
LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BCMOCPT T2 ON 
T1.T01CD=T2.T01CD AND 
T1.T09CD=T2.T09CD AND 
T1.MOVNUREG=T2.MOVNUREG AND 
T1.MOVNRIRE=T2.MOVNRIRE AND 
T2.MOCPROV='1'

Processing command file K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\5.0.0\fix\V5R1M0/42211/primrose/script/01VisteTHPDA.TDDML.
DROP VIEW FINANCE.THPDAVA
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.THPDAVA AS 
SELECT 
T1.ID_AZIENDA, 
T1.ID_ANNO_DOC, 
T1.ID_NUMERO_DOC, 
COALESCE(T1.NUMERO_FATTURA, ' ') AS NUMERO_FATTURA, 
COALESCE(T1.R_CAU_DOC_ACQ, ' ') AS R_CAU_DOC_ACQ, 
COALESCE(T1.R_FORNITORE, ' ') AS R_FORNITORE, 
COALESCE(T1.R_FORNITORE_FAT, ' ') AS R_FORNITORE_FAT, 
COALESCE(T1.R_FOR_PRN, ' ') AS R_FOR_PRN, 
COALESCE(T1.R_MAGAZZINO, ' ') AS R_MAGAZZINO, 
COALESCE(T1.ANNO_FAT, ' ') AS ANNO_FAT, 
T1.STATO_AVANZAMENTO, 
COALESCE(T1.DATA_FATTURA, CONVERT(DATETIME, '1753-01-01', 120)) AS DATA_FATTURA, 
COALESCE(T1.R_VALUTA, ' ') AS R_VALUTA, 
COALESCE(T1.R_ASSOG_IVA, ' ') AS R_ASSOG_IVA, 
COALESCE(T1.R_MOD_PAGAMENTO, ' ') AS R_MOD_PAGAMENTO,
COALESCE(T1.FATTORE_CAMBI, 0) AS FATTORE_CAMBI,
T1.COL_CONTABILITA, 
T1.TP_DOC_ACQ, 
COALESCE(T1.R_FOR_DEN, ' ') AS R_FOR_DEN, 
COALESCE(T1.R_CLI_DEN, ' ') AS R_CLI_DEN, 
COALESCE(T1.DATA_INIZIO_PAG, CONVERT(DATETIME, '1753-01-01', 120)) AS DATA_INIZIO_PAG, 
T1.STATO, 
COALESCE(T1.DATA_RIF_FOR, CONVERT(DATETIME, '1753-01-01', 120)) AS DATA_RIF_FOR 
FROM THIP.DOC_ACQ_TES T1
GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.THPDAVA TO PUBLIC

Processing command file K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\5.0.0\fix\V5R1M0/42223/tddml/ORD_ESEC_ATV_V02.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.ORD_ESEC_ATV_V02
CREATE 
					VIEW THIP.ORD_ESEC_ATV_V02 AS 
				SELECT 
					ORD.ID_AZIENDA ID_AZIENDA, 
					ORD.ID_ANNO_ORD ID_ANNO_ORD, 
					ORD.ID_NUMERO_ORD ID_NUMERO_ORD, 
					ORD.R_ARTICOLO R_ARTICOLO, 
					ORD.R_VERSIONE R_VERSIONE, 
					ORD.R_CONFIGURAZIONE R_CONFIGURAZIONE, 
					ORD.DESCRIZIONE DESCRIZIONE, 
					ORD.R_UM_PRM_MAG ORD_UM_PRM, 
					ORD.R_COMMESSA R_COMMESSA, 
					ORD.R_MAGAZZINO_PRL R_MAGAZZINO_PRL, 
					ORD.R_MAGAZZINO_VRS R_MAGAZZINO_VRS, 
					ORD.R_RESPONSABILE R_RESPONSABILE, 
					ORD.R_CLIENTE R_CLIENTE, 
					ORD.STATO_SCHEDUL STATO_SCHEDUL, 
					ART.R_LINEA_PROD R_LINEA_PROD, 
					ART.R_MACROFAMIGLIA R_MACROFAMIGLIA, 
					ART.R_SUBFAMIGLIA R_SUBFAMIGLIA, 
					ART.R_MICROFAMIGLIA R_MICROFAMIGLIA, 
					ART.R_PIANIFICATORE R_PIANIFICATORE,
					ATV.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA, 
					ATV.NUM_RITORNO NUM_RITORNO, 
					ATV.R_OPERAZIONE R_OPERAZIONE, 
					ATV.R_ATTIVITA R_ATTIVITA, 
					ATV.R_STABILIMENTO R_STABILIMENTO, 
					ATV.R_REPARTO R_REPARTO, 
					ATV.R_CENTRO_LAVORO R_CENTRO_LAVORO, 
					ATV.DATA_INIZIO_EFF DATA_INIZIO_EFF, 
					ATV.DATA_INIZIO_PGM DATA_INIZIO_PGM, 
					ORD.DATA_INIZIO_RCS DATA_INIZIO_RCS, 
					ATV.ORA_INIZIO_EFF ORA_INIZIO_EFF, 
					ATV.ORA_INIZIO_PGM ORA_INIZIO_PGM, 
					ATV.DATA_FINE_EFF DATA_FINE_EFF, 
					ATV.DATA_FINE_PGM DATA_FINE_PGM, 
					ORD.DATA_FINE_RCS DATA_FINE_RCS, 
					ATV.QTA_RCS_UM_PRM QTA_RCS_ATV, 
					CASE 
						WHEN ATV.STATO_ATTIV >= '4' 
							THEN 0 
						WHEN ATV.QTA_RCS_UM_PRM > (COALESCE(ATV.QTA_PRD_UM_PRM,0) + COALESCE(ATV.QTA_SCA_UM_PRM,0)) 
							THEN (ATV.QTA_RCS_UM_PRM - (COALESCE(ATV.QTA_PRD_UM_PRM,0) + COALESCE(ATV.QTA_SCA_UM_PRM,0))) 
						ELSE 0 
					END QTA_RES_ATV, 
					MAT.ID_RIGA_MATERIALE ID_RIGA_MATERIALE, 
					MAT.R_ARTICOLO R_ARTICOLO_MAT, 
					MAT.R_VERSIONE R_VERSIONE_MAT, 
					MAT.R_CONFIGURAZIONE R_CONFIGURAZIONE_MAT, 
					MAT.R_COMMESSA R_COMMESSA_MAT, 
					MAT.R_MAGAZZINO_PRL R_MAGAZZINO_MAT, 
					MAT.DATA_PRV_IMPIEGO DATA_PRV_IMPIEGO, 
					(SELECT MIN(DATA_PRV_IMPIEGO) FROM THIP.ORDESE_ATV_MAT WHERE 
                                        ATV.ID_AZIENDA = THIP.ORDESE_ATV_MAT.ID_AZIENDA
		             AND ATV.ID_ANNO_ORD = THIP.ORDESE_ATV_MAT.ID_ANNO_ORD 
		             AND ATV.ID_NUMERO_ORD = THIP.ORDESE_ATV_MAT.ID_NUMERO_ORD 
		             AND ATV.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA = THIP.ORDESE_ATV_MAT.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA)
		            MIN_DATA_PRV_IMP, 
					MAT.R_UM_PRM_MAG MAT_UM_PRM, 
					MAT.R_UM_SEC_MAG MAT_UM_SEC, 
					MAT.COEFF_IMPIEGO COEFF_IMPIEGO, 
					MAT.COEFF_TOTALE COEFF_TOTALE, 
					MAT.QTA_RCS_UM_PRM QTA_RCS_MAT,
                                        ARTMAT.R_CLS_ABC_MAG,
					MAG.MAGAZZINO_LINEA, 
					LOT.ID_LOTTO ID_LOTTO, 
					LOT.QTA_RCS_UM_PRM QTA_RCS_PRM_LT, 
					CASE 
						WHEN LOT.STATO_LOTTO = '2' 
							THEN 0 
						WHEN LOT.STATO_LOTTO < '2' AND LOT.QTA_RCS_UM_PRM > COALESCE(LOT.QTA_PRL_UM_PRM,0) 
							THEN (LOT.QTA_RCS_UM_PRM - COALESCE(LOT.QTA_PRL_UM_PRM,0)) 
						ELSE 0 
					END QTA_RES_PRM_LT, 
					CASE 
						WHEN LOT.STATO_LOTTO = '2' 
							THEN 0 
						WHEN LOT.STATO_LOTTO < '2' AND COALESCE(LOT.QTA_RCS_UM_SEC,0) > COALESCE(LOT.QTA_PRL_UM_SEC,0) 
							THEN (COALESCE(LOT.QTA_RCS_UM_SEC,0) - COALESCE(LOT.QTA_PRL_UM_SEC,0)) 
						ELSE 0 
					END QTA_RES_SEC_LT 
				FROM 
					THIP.ORD_ESEC ORD 
				INNER JOIN 
					THIP.ARTICOLI ART ON 
					ORD.ID_AZIENDA    = ART.ID_AZIENDA 
					AND ORD.R_ARTICOLO= ART.ID_ARTICOLO 
				INNER JOIN 
					THIP.ORD_ESEC_ATV ATV ON 
					ORD.ID_AZIENDA       = ATV.ID_AZIENDA 
					AND ORD.ID_ANNO_ORD  = ATV.ID_ANNO_ORD 
					AND ORD.ID_NUMERO_ORD= ATV.ID_NUMERO_ORD 
				INNER JOIN 
					THIP.ORDESE_ATV_MAT MAT ON 
					ATV.ID_AZIENDA          = MAT.ID_AZIENDA 
					AND ATV.ID_ANNO_ORD     = MAT.ID_ANNO_ORD 
					AND ATV.ID_NUMERO_ORD   = MAT.ID_NUMERO_ORD 
					AND ATV.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA= MAT.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA 
				LEFT OUTER JOIN 
					THIP.ORDESE_ATV_LTM LOT ON 
					MAT.ID_AZIENDA           = LOT.ID_AZIENDA 
					AND MAT.ID_ANNO_ORD      = LOT.ID_ANNO_ORD 
					AND MAT.ID_NUMERO_ORD    = LOT.ID_NUMERO_ORD 
					AND MAT.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA = LOT.ID_RIGA_ATTIVITA 
					AND MAT.ID_RIGA_MATERIALE= LOT.ID_RIGA_MATERIALE 
				LEFT OUTER JOIN 
					THIP.MAGAZZINI MAG ON 
					MAT.ID_AZIENDA           = MAG.ID_AZIENDA 
					AND MAT.R_MAGAZZINO_PRL  = MAG.ID_MAGAZZINO 
                              INNER JOIN 
					THIP.ARTICOLI ARTMAT ON 
					MAT.ID_AZIENDA       = ARTMAT.ID_AZIENDA 
					AND MAT.R_ARTICOLO  = ARTMAT.ID_ARTICOLO
				WHERE 
					ORD.STATO             = 'V' 
					AND ATV.STATO         = 'V' 
					AND MAT.STATO         = 'V' 
					AND MAT.MOD_PRELIEVO  = '0' 
					AND ORD.STATO_ORDINE IN ('1', '2', '3')
					AND MAG.MAGAZZINO_LINEA = 'N'

Processing command file K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\5.0.0\fix\NODB.SQL.
E' stata applicata la fix 42223
